item.title: CVE-2019-0344|2024-10-04T13:36:02.145Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20commerce%20cloud%20%28virtualjdbc%20extension%29
item.description: Due to unsafe deserialization used in SAP Commerce Cloud (virtualjdbc extension), versions 6.4, 6.5, 6.6, 6.7, 1808, 1811, 1905, it is possible to execute arbitrary code on a target machine with 'Hybris' user rights, resulting in Code Injection.
